videos.description: 1H (0:01) TLSA Sterling Taplin made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Marquel Curtis.
videos.headline: S. Taplin made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by M. Curtis.

videos.description: Tulsa's Sterling Taplin looks like he's going for the long three behind the line but instead makes the perfect pass to D'Andre Wright for the alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: 3-point shot? Nope! It's alley-oop time

videos.description: Tulsa's Sterling Taplin cuts to the hoop and spinning backwards, throws the ball off the window to Rashad Smith for the alley-oop flush.
videos.headline: Reverse off-the-backboard alley-oop? Yes please!
